<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Selected_scholarly_articles">Selected scholarly articles</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Joseph_Stiglitz&amp;action=edit&amp;section=46" title="Edit section: Selected scholarly articles">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>
<p><small>1970–1979</small></p>
<ul>
