gory:Gerald_Loeb_Award_winners" title="Category:Gerald Loeb Award winners">Gerald Loeb Award winners</a></li><li><a href="/wiki/Category:Guggenheim_Fellows" title="Category:Guggenheim Fellows">Guggenheim Fellows</a></li><li><a href="/wiki/Category:Information_economists" title="Category:Information economists">Information economists</a></li><li><a href="/wiki/Category:Intergovernmental_Panel_on_Climate_Change_lead_authors" title="Category:Intergovernmental Panel on Climate Change lead authors">Intergovernmental Panel on Climate Change lead authors</a></li><li><a href="/wiki/Category:Jewish_American_social_scientists" title="Category:Jewish American social scientists">Jewish American social scientists</a></li><li><a href="/wiki/Category:Jewish_American_writers" title="Category:Jewish American writers">Jewish American writers</a></li><li><a href="/wiki/Category:Keio_University_faculty" title="Category:Keio University faculty">Keio University faculty</a></li><li><a href="/wiki/Category:Keynesians" title="Category:Keynesians">Keynesians</a></li><li><a href="/wiki/Category:Labour_Party_(UK)_people" title="Category:Labour Party (UK) people">Labour Party (UK) people</a></li><li><a href="/wiki/Category:Living_people" title="Category:Living people">Living people</a></li><li><a href="/wiki/Category:Massachusetts_Institute_of_Technology_alumni" title="Category:Massachusetts Institute of Technology alumni">Massachusetts Institute of Technology alumni</a></li><li><a href="/wiki/Category:Institute_for_Advanced_Study_visiting_scholars" title="Category:Institute for Advanced Study visiting scholars">Institute for Advanced Study visiting scholars</a></li><li><a href="/wiki/Category:Members_of_the_Pontifical_Academy_of_Social_Sciences" title="Category:Members of the Pontifical Academy of Social Sciences">Members of the Pontifical Academy of Social Sciences</a></li><li><a href="/wiki/Category:Members_of_the_United_States_National_Academy_of_Sciences" title="Category:Members of the Uni